Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.54,0:00:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[NARRATOR]\NWealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.45,0:00:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold Roger, the King\Nof the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.12,0:00:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,attained this and everything\Nelse the world had to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.92,0:00:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And his dying words drove\Ncountless souls to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.42,0:00:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[GOLD ROGER]\NYou want my treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.01,0:00:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.30,0:00:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I left everything I gathered\Ntogether in one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.64,0:00:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you just have to find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.72,0:00:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[NARRATOR] These words lured men\Nto the Grand Line in pursuit
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.93,0:00:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,of dreams greater than\Nthey've ever dared to imagine!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.52,0:00:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the time known\Nas the Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.82,0:00:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come aboard and bring along{\i0}\N{\i1}all your hopes and dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.40,0:00:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together we will find everything{\i0}\N{\i1}that we're looking for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.16,0:00:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One Piece!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.42,0:01:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Compass left behind{\i0}\N{\i1}It'll only slow us down{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.88,0:01:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your heart will be your guide{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.13,0:01:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Raise the sails{\i0}\N{\i1}and take the helm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.51,0:01:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That legendary place that the{\i0}\N{\i1}end of the map reveals{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.14,0:01:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is only legendary{\i0}\N{\i1}until someone proves it real{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.90,0:01:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Through it all, through all{\i0}\N{\i1}the troubled times,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.90,0:01:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}through the heartache,{\i0}\N{\i1}and through the pain{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.61,0:01:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Know that I will be there{\i0}\N{\i1}to stand by you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.87,0:01:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just like I know{\i0}\N{\i1}you'll stand by me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.37,0:01:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So come aboard and bring along{\i0}\N{\i1}all your hopes and dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.04,0:01:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together we will find everything{\i0}\N{\i1}that we're looking for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.92,0:01:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's always room for you{\i0}\N{\i1}if you want to be my friend{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.89,0:02:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are, we are on the cruise{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.44,0:02:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.56,0:02:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[seagulls squawking]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.90,0:02:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What a day!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.73,0:02:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gorgeous!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.03,0:02:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as we can\Nstay on this heading,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.74,0:02:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,we should reach the Marine\NBase in no time at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.24,0:02:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] Wow, Coby!\NYou're great out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.41,0:02:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean we're actually gonna
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.45,0:02:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,reach the place we\Noriginally set out for?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.54,0:02:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY]\NOf course. It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.83,0:02:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just using the skills that\Nevery sailor should have.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.25,0:02:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.62,0:02:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, there's really\Nnothing to be so giggly about.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.09,0:02:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.92,0:02:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,...at the Marine Base...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.96,0:02:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,...they're holding the\Ngreat pirate hunter...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.30,0:02:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Roronoa Zoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.93,0:02:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY] This is the man\Nwho's diced up his bounties
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.22,0:02:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,like a an animal bent on\Ncarnage, a blood thirsty beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.69,0:02:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been called nothing less
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.19,0:02:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,than a living, breathing\Ndemon in human form.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.86,0:02:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\N"Enter the Great Swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.90,0:02:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirate Hunter Roronoa Zoro!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.66,0:03:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.46,0:03:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The Marine Base city!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.67,0:03:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy, seriously,\Nyou're out of your mind
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.63,0:03:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,if you think the right thing to\Ndo is get this guy to join you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.22,0:03:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I haven't\Nmade up my mind yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.89,0:03:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta see if he's a good guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.43,0:03:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He's imprisoned because\Nhe's obviously not!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.31,0:03:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] Hey, is that guy\NZoro around here somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.36,0:03:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[WOMAN A gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.15,0:03:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[CROWD screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.61,0:03:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[CROWD whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.15,0:03:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we shouldn't mention\Nthe name Zoro here, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.99,0:03:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's head to the base\Nand check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.74,0:03:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna be a Marine, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.91,0:03:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, of course I do, Luffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.29,0:03:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,but I really don't think\NI'm ready just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.46,0:03:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,From what I've heard, the\Nman in charge of this base
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.67,0:03:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,is named Captain Morgan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[CROWD screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.38,0:03:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[CROWD whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.47,0:03:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.47,0:04:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This town is such a weird place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY]\NThat was odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.18,0:04:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I understand if\Nthey're scared of Zoro,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.10,0:04:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,but why did they flip
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.93,0:04:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,when I mentioned the\NMarine Captain's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.39,0:04:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know... I've got\Na bad feeling about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.44,0:04:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe they were all just jumpin'\Naround for the fun of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.02,0:04:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And how would that\Nmake any sense?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.36,0:04:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NThis looks like the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.15,0:04:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I made it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.61,0:04:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[cries]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.99,0:04:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where you\Nand I part ways, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.33,0:04:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't have long\Ntogether but--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.29,0:04:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.95,0:04:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NWhere's the foothold?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.00,0:04:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY]\NGet down from there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.00,0:04:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you doing?!\NThey'll see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.87,0:04:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Now where's this demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.96,0:04:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY] They wouldn't\Nkeep him out in the open.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.67,0:04:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He's probably tucked in a\Nprison cell below ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.38,0:04:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NThere he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.17,0:04:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh. I'm gonna get closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.51,0:04:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Coby, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.80,0:04:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.55,0:04:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you he's not-- Uh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.48,0:04:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY]\NThat hood on his head...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.52,0:04:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,...and a haramaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.02,0:04:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Roronoa Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.11,0:05:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If we untie those ropes,\Nhe can just walk away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.61,0:05:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't be such\Nan idiot, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.87,0:05:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no telling what\Na bandit like him will do
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.95,0:05:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,if you let him go!\NHe might just kill us both!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.75,0:05:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I'm strong.\NI can protect us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.96,0:05:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY]\NHe's lost his mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.42,0:05:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NHey, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.79,0:05:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.96,0:05:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You're an eyesore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.80,0:05:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.88,0:05:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.18,0:05:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY] Luffy, trust me,\Nthere's no chance you'll survive
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.93,0:05:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,with someone like\Nhim on your crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.18,0:05:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[RIKA]\NShh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.02,0:05:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,[RIKA grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.40,0:05:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.23,0:05:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY yelps]\NLuffy, we gotta stop her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.98,0:05:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll be killed! Either by the\NMarines or the demon himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.95,0:05:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NWhaddya want?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.70,0:05:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you might\Nbe getting hungry now,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.70,0:05:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,so I made you a\Ncouple of rice balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.62,0:05:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You got a death wish, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.49,0:05:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Just scram.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.37,0:05:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[RIKA]\NBut you haven't eaten anything
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.66,0:05:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,the whole time\Nyou've been tied up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.33,0:05:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.29,0:05:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never really\Nmade them before...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.75,0:05:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...but I did my best,\Nso I think they're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.17,0:06:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, kid, I'm not hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.76,0:06:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Now stop irritating me,\Nand get outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.05,0:06:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[RIKA]\NBut--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.72,0:06:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not make me kick\Nyour ass, little girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.51,0:06:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[HELMEPPO]\NNow, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.51,0:06:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No one likes a bully.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.06,0:06:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.06,0:06:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,[HELMEPPO chuckles]\NRoronoa Zoro,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.93,0:06:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,you seem to be\Nhandling this well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.35,0:06:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.11,0:06:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look. Now there's\Nanother weird guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.36,0:06:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He must be with the Marines.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.28,0:06:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we know the\Ngirl will be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.40,0:06:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Looky, some tasty rice balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.82,0:06:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[RIKA]\NThat's not for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.70,0:06:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[HELMEPPO gasps, screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.29,0:06:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Too sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.45,0:06:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,They're packed with sugar!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're supposed to use\Nsalt, you idiot, salt!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.46,0:06:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.38,0:06:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought they'd\Ntaste better sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.34,0:06:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,--[HELMEPPO] Gimme that!\N--[RIKA yelps]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.17,0:06:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[HELMEPPO grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.38,0:06:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[RIKA]\NNo! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.63,0:06:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,--[RIKA] I worked so hard!\N--That's just awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.63,0:06:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[HELMEPPO grunts, sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.22,0:06:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[RIKA cries]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.14,0:06:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.89,0:06:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...worked so hard\Nto make those...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.98,0:06:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.31,0:06:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You must've not read\Nthe notice that was posted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.31,0:07:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who assist criminals\Nin any way will be executed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.53,0:07:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Signed, Marine Captain Morgan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.49,0:07:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[RIKA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.61,0:07:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.11,0:07:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems even little\Nbrats fear my daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.66,0:07:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,His daddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.33,0:07:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So that guy's father\Nis Captain Morgan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.95,0:07:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.66,0:07:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Toss this kid out right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.00,0:07:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,[MARINE A gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.83,0:07:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, throw her\Nover the wall, soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.50,0:07:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Now if you won't\Nfollow my orders,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.42,0:07:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.01,0:07:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir! I-I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.51,0:07:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[RIKA whimpers, gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.72,0:07:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[RIKA]\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.55,0:07:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about this.\NTry curling up into a ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.81,0:07:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[RIKA gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,--[RIKA screams]\N--[LUFFY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.18,0:07:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[RIKA screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.64,0:07:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.44,0:07:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.11,0:07:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY]\NLuffy! Are you two okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.57,0:07:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, little girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.90,0:07:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.82,0:07:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe how\Nwretched a person he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.45,0:07:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Now where are you\Nhurt? Anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.03,0:07:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.87,0:07:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[HELMEPPO laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.04,0:07:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[HELMEPPO snorts, laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.79,0:08:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just dead set on\Nstaying alive, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.79,0:08:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.50,0:08:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm gonna make it through\Nthe month without any problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.80,0:08:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Right... Good luck with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.71,0:08:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[HELMEPPO laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.97,0:08:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Only ten days left.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.80,0:08:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[HELMEPPO] Oh, you still\Nassume you'll make it
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.26,0:08:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,to the end of those ten days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.85,0:08:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[HELMEPPO laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.47,0:08:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY]\NHow can that man be so cruel?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.18,0:08:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.31,0:08:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh! What the--?\NWhere did he go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.15,0:08:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.57,0:08:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NSo, I hear you're a bad guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.73,0:08:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NAre you still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.15,0:08:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NYou're stuck out here
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.07,0:08:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,for all the world\Nto see and nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.11,0:08:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really all that strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.41,0:08:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NMind your own business!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.78,0:08:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.62,0:08:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were you, I'd probably\Nstarve to death in three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.71,0:08:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] I've got more spirit\Nthan you could ever have,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.75,0:08:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,which is how I'm gonna\Nsurvive this ordeal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.34,0:08:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This I swear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.30,0:08:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hah, what a weirdo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.38,0:08:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.89,0:08:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you... pick\Nthat up for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.35,0:08:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna eat this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.35,0:08:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cause it's mostly\Na ball of mud.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.27,0:09:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up and give it to me, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.23,0:09:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NUh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.65,0:09:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO coughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.44,0:09:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Should've listened to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.11,0:09:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NIt was good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.24,0:09:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.41,0:09:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,[RIKA]\NReally?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.20,0:09:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,He ate every last\Ngrain of rice there was.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.91,0:09:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.33,0:09:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Zoro\Nwas really as evil
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.33,0:09:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,as everyone\Nthinks that he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.92,0:09:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.75,0:09:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He's good... because...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.67,0:09:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He got himself punished...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.30,0:09:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,...for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.34,0:09:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're, uh... You're\Nmaking no sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.68,0:09:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.76,0:09:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that dumb Helmeppo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.64,0:09:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the son of Captain Morgan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.06,0:09:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,[HELMEPPO]\NStep aside! Step aside!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.27,0:09:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Make way for my\Nbeautiful pet doggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.77,0:09:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone who doesn't move,\NI'll have executed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.57,0:09:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[HELMEPPO laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.28,0:09:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,--[WOLF roars]\N--[CROWD screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.11,0:09:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[RIKA screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.66,0:09:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,[MAN screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.45,0:09:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, you mean ol' thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.16,0:10:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You, little girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.62,0:10:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there some kind of problem
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.79,0:10:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,with how my beloved\Ndog is behaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.04,0:10:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Rika, put it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.38,0:10:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want to\Nget us in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[HELMEPPO snickering]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.84,0:10:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,--[WOLF roars]\N--[RIKA screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.01,0:10:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[HELMEPPO screams, gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.76,0:10:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[CROWD chattering]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.56,0:10:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.72,0:10:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! You're him... It's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.68,0:10:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the Pirate Hunter Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.73,0:10:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NAnd if I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.44,0:10:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What is a pirate hunter doing\Ndefying the Marines, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.69,0:10:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] Can it, and let me\Nfinish my meal in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.19,0:10:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.11,0:10:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[HELMEPPO grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.41,0:10:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,[screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.57,0:10:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,[HELMEPPO groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.00,0:10:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.96,0:10:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] You're getting\Non my nerves, pal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.17,0:10:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You and that precious\Nmutt of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.71,0:10:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.96,0:10:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.55,0:10:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You do realize...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.18,0:10:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,...if my dad finds\Nout about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.64,0:11:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,...he'll surely execute\Nthe girl and her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.89,0:11:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha. So what do you say\Nto a little deal between men?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.94,0:11:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,In place of the kid and her mom,\Nwe string you up instead...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.07,0:11:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,...for, uh, say one month!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.57,0:11:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You survive that one month,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.99,0:11:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'll be so nice\Nas to let you live, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.91,0:11:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Whaddya say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.78,0:11:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sound fair?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.79,0:11:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Then one month it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.33,0:11:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[RIKA] It's been three\Nweeks since that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.34,0:11:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Helmeppo keeps punching and\Nkicking him while he's tied up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.59,0:11:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He's being so unfair!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.26,0:11:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.80,0:11:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how to help him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.26,0:11:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,--[RIKA cries]\N--I see why you're upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.97,0:11:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,[glass shattering]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.85,0:11:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.77,0:11:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring us whatever you got and\Nkeep the check for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.64,0:11:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.15,0:11:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And bring me a bottle\Nof your finest moonshine
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.11,0:11:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,or whatever crap you serve.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.77,0:11:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And put some speed to it,\Nlady; I don't have all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.74,0:11:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... That's more like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.82,0:11:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to think of\Nsomething interesting to do
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.74,0:12:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,seeing as how I'm bored\Nout of my skull here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.24,0:12:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose I can execute Zoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.33,0:12:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[HELMEPPO cackling
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[HELMEPPO groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.63,0:12:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You... You just hit me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.21,0:12:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY]\NLuffy, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.13,0:12:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't hit him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.38,0:12:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy is scum!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.01,0:12:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You actually hit me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.05,0:12:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Captain Morgan's\Nson, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.64,0:12:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NYeah, like I care!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.14,0:12:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll care after he\Nexecutes you for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.98,0:12:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just\Nbe a man and fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.94,0:12:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy, just ease off some.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.52,0:12:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you trying to get\Non the Marines' bad side?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.69,0:12:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NI've made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.90,0:12:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.69,0:12:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Today...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.40,0:12:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoro joins my crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.03,0:12:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[MORGAN]\NI am...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.00,0:12:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,...great!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.45,0:12:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[MARINE B]\NYes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.16,0:12:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You are right,\NCaptain Morgan, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.08,0:12:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[MORGAN] And yet, the taxes\Nwe collect don't even compare
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.92,0:12:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,to my sheer degree of greatness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.88,0:12:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, right, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.05,0:12:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that the\Ncitizens' wallets
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.63,0:13:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,just aren't very deep\Nthese days, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.76,0:13:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[MORGAN]\NThe issue at hand here
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.18,0:13:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,is their level of\Nrespect for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.43,0:13:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.47,0:13:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[HELMEPPO sobbing]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.47,0:13:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,--Daddy!\N--[MORGAN] Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.81,0:13:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,There's someone outside that\NI want you to slaughter,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.31,0:13:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and I want it done now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.84,0:13:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,--[wood clattering]\N--[ZORO groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.55,0:13:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.13,0:13:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[KUINA]\NHah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.89,0:13:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NAh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.47,0:13:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You're weak, Zoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.81,0:13:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing ever changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.27,0:13:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NI made a promise to her...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.56,0:13:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And I can't afford to\Ndie in a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.36,0:14:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.78,0:14:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[sighs]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.20,0:14:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.99,0:14:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You again...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.04,0:14:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have things to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.37,0:14:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll untie you, but only if\Nyou promise to join my crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.33,0:14:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Your what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.42,0:14:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I run a pirate crew, and I'm\Nlooking for people to join up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.96,0:14:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.92,0:14:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd never stoop to\Njoining up with a criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.72,0:14:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Screw that business.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.09,0:14:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And what's wrong\Nwith being a pirate?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.26,0:14:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,They're despicable!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.14,0:14:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I'd ever wanna\Njoin up with one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.64,0:14:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on! Gimme a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.18,0:14:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone already knows you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.31,0:14:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,as some viscious bounty hunter\Nalways out for blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.02,0:14:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,People can say whatever\Nthey want about me,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.44,0:14:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,but I've never done a single\Nthing in my life that I regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.07,0:14:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I will make it through\Nthis challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.40,0:14:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And after that, I'll\Naccomplish what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.41,0:14:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've already decided that\Nyou're going to be on my crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.41,0:14:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! You can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.83,0:14:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear you're one of\Nthe best swordsmen around.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.87,0:14:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NWell, I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.92,0:14:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But that idiot Captain's\Nson took mine away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.79,0:15:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess I'll just have to\Ngo get it back for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.55,0:15:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.25,0:15:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you want your sword,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.80,0:15:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,you're just gonna\Nhave to join my crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.51,0:15:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you're really\Npissing me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.18,0:15:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.80,0:15:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait... he's actually\Ngonna bust in there alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.39,0:15:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.35,0:15:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The base is in the\Nother direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.85,0:15:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.52,0:15:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum Gum Rocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.44,0:15:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.77,0:15:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.74,0:15:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[MARINES]\NHeave ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.36,0:15:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Heave ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.12,0:15:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Heave ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.54,0:15:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[MORGAN]\NThat's it! Stop right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.75,0:15:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Now stand it up\Nin one final pull!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.21,0:15:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.08,0:15:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you gonna get revenge\Non this guy or what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.38,0:15:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean he just outright\Nstruck me in public!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.05,0:15:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You never hit me before!\NWhy should he be able to?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.97,0:15:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[MORGAN]\NDo you have any remote idea
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.72,0:15:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,as to why I've never hit you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.89,0:15:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.72,0:15:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Is it because\Nyou think I'm great?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.10,0:15:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,[MORGAN]\NNo...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.64,0:16:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.31,0:16:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[HELMEPPO screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.36,0:16:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[HELMEPPO groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.94,0:16:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[MORGAN]\NYou're a stupid fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.74,0:16:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,...who isn't even worth hitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.95,0:16:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want you to\Nget the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.00,0:16:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The only great one around here
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.04,0:16:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,is the man you call your father!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.04,0:16:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[HELMEPPO groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.67,0:16:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[MORGAN]\NWhich reminds me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.01,0:16:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard a rat snuck into\Nthe crucifixion yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.13,0:16:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[HELMEPPO gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.09,0:16:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. That's right, the little\Ngirl, but I had her dealt with.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.51,0:16:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope that means killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.14,0:16:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I...I didn't kill her.\NShe's just a kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.23,0:16:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[MORGAN]\NYou there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.19,0:16:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Go into town, find this\Ngirl, and kill her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.86,0:16:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But... sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.23,0:16:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be serious...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.82,0:16:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,She's just a little girl, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.36,0:16:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[MORGAN] I don't care\Nif she's a child or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.49,0:16:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone who disobeys\Nmy orders is a traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.37,0:16:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,[LIEUTENANT]\NNo, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.99,0:16:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.58,0:16:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[MORGAN growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.37,0:16:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[MORGAN grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.75,0:17:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[HELMEPPO screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.08,0:17:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[MARINES]\NLieutenant!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.79,0:17:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You... You killed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.21,0:17:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,My strength was what I used\Nto rise to the rank of captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.88,0:17:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.01,0:17:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,In this world,\Ntitles are what matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.64,0:17:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That means by being the\Ncaptain of this base
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.05,0:17:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and the highest ranking officer,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.93,0:17:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the most superior person\Nas far as the eye can see!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.64,0:17:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This means...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.15,0:17:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,that I do everything right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.48,0:17:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I correct, men?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.11,0:17:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[MARINES]\NSir! You are correct, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.11,0:17:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's put killing the\Ngirl on hold for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.91,0:17:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Observe,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.86,0:17:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,the greatest symbol of\Nmy unending authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It took years to\Ncomplete, but here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.37,0:17:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,--Now stand it up!\N--[MARINES] Heave ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.67,0:17:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[MORGAN]\NDisplay my greatness at
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.29,0:17:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,the top of this\Nbase for all to see!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.01,0:17:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.09,0:17:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nobody here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.43,0:17:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta find that\Ncrazy idiot son
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.39,0:17:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and get Zoro's sword\Nback for him. Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.60,0:17:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,--[MARINES] Heave ho!\N--[MORGAN] Pull men!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.47,0:17:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,--Heave ho!\N--Harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.77,0:18:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,[MARINES]\NHeave ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,[MORGAN]\NYou there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.36,0:18:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[MARINE E whimpers]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.32,0:18:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You bumped it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.57,0:18:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.94,0:18:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like something's\Ngoin' on up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.41,0:18:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.62,0:18:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I was reckless!\NI didn't mean it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.33,0:18:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[MORGAN] I consider the\Nslightest scratch on this...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.16,0:18:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...nothing less...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.54,0:18:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...than a traitorous activity\Nthat's punishable by death!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.88,0:18:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess I should check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.25,0:18:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.13,0:18:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,...Rocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.92,0:18:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,--[MARINE E screams]\N--[MORGAN yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.63,0:18:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHuh-hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.68,0:18:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Wah... I jumped too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.30,0:18:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[MORGAN]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.97,0:18:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.22,0:18:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It flew up from the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.27,0:18:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,--[LUFFY] Got it!\N--[MARINES gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.98,0:18:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[MARINES screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.69,0:18:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[MARINES grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.86,0:18:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[MORGAN gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.69,0:18:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,[HELMEPPO, MARINES scream]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.11,0:18:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NUh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.03,0:18:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NSorry 'bout that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.07,0:19:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Seize him and hold him,\Nso I can kill him myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.91,0:19:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,[MARINES]\NSir! Right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.37,0:19:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's him! That's the guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.66,0:19:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the one
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.33,0:19:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,--who punched me, daddy!\N--[LUFFY] Hey, it's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.42,0:19:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.38,0:19:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been looking for\Nyou all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.29,0:19:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You have something that\NI really need to get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.80,0:19:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,--[HELMEPPO] Let me go!\N--[MARINES] Helmeppo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.84,0:19:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[HELMEPPO]\NSomeone help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.55,0:19:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,[MORGAN]\NDo not let that man escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.88,0:19:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[MARINE J]\NCaptain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.51,0:19:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,There's someone in\Nthe crucifixion yard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.39,0:19:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.23,0:19:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surrounded... by traitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.44,0:19:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,[GIRL grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.98,0:19:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[MARINE K]\NAfter him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.15,0:19:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.94,0:19:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,[MARINE L]\NSir, yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.24,0:19:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's rocking the boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.20,0:19:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[HELMEPPO screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.08,0:19:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so tell me where\NZoro's sword is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.04,0:19:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[HELMEPPO]\NI'll tell you! I promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.66,0:19:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Just please stop dragging\Nme across the carpet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.33,0:19:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, which way?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.25,0:19:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,In my room. We just passed it,\Nbehind you on the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.55,0:19:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you say so earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.51,0:19:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we gotta go\Nall the way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.17,0:19:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.22,0:19:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Except for letting Helmeppo go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.14,0:20:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.89,0:20:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can try\Nshooting me if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.35,0:20:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[HELMEPPO]\NNo! Please don't shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.06,0:20:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't-- Get the\Nhell outta the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.69,0:20:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY] You have to\Nget out of here, Zoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.81,0:20:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That maniac's going to kill you\Nfor what you're doin' right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.57,0:20:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY]\NI can't stand to watch
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.86,0:20:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,the Marines behave\Nlike this anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.90,0:20:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,A true Marine\Nshould be honorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.53,0:20:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, kid, I can't leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.24,0:20:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I got ten days left.\NAnd, then they're--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.24,0:20:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, not quite. They're\Ngonna execute you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.66,0:20:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,They're what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.54,0:20:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY] Helmeppo never intended\Nto honor your agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.12,0:20:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He planned on killing\Nyou from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.33,0:20:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Which made Luffy really angry,\Nso he just knocked him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.21,0:20:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He did?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.34,0:20:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that the Marines are mad,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.55,0:20:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,they're dead set\Non catching Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.09,0:20:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I'm not gonna ask\Nyou to become a pirate, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.26,0:20:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But I hope you'll help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.02,0:20:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a lotta\Nstrength you can offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.61,0:20:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY]\NLuffy's the only person here
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.23,0:20:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,who can actually save\Nyou from execution.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.07,0:20:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.57,0:21:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the only one\Nhere who can save him
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.99,0:21:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,from a very similar fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.08,0:21:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[MORGAN]\NEnd of the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.54,0:21:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[MORGAN] For the crime\Nof treason against me,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.29,0:21:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I sentence you both\Nto die where you stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.34,0:21:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY yelps]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.34,0:21:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This looks like yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.26,0:21:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NBingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.43,0:21:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on. There are three here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.31,0:21:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, weirdo, which one\Nof these is Zoro's?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.35,0:21:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,--[HELMEPPO whimpering]\N--[LUFFY] Guess he passed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.02,0:21:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.90,0:21:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NCoby!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.06,0:21:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,[COBY whimpering]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.11,0:21:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been pulling some\Ninteresting moves around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.12,0:21:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this? Some kind\Nof poorly executed coup
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.95,0:21:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,you two planned\Nwith the straw hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.54,0:21:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] I've always fought\Nalone like a real man does.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.17,0:21:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Not like a coward...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.58,0:21:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...who hides behind his\Nwall of expendable cronies.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.63,0:22:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[MORGAN]\NRoronoa Zoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.51,0:22:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare underestimate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.26,0:22:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You may be a strong fighter,\Nbut under my authority,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.47,0:22:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,you're just the rat we\Nthrow out with the trash.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.31,0:22:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Take aim!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.68,0:22:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NNo...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.81,0:22:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NI can't afford to die here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.57,0:22:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're weak, Zoro...\NNothing ever changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.86,0:22:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.32,0:22:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NGum Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.95,0:22:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...Rocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.83,0:22:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.50,0:22:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.00,0:22:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,--[ZORO] What?!\N--Luffy, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.33,0:22:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.50,0:22:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[MARINE gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.84,0:22:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY laughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.80,0:22:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.14,0:22:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.39,0:22:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That won't work on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.97,0:22:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Told ya I was strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.31,0:22:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What the--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.73,0:22:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.98,0:22:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,My name's Monkey D. Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.48,0:23:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm gonna be\NKing of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.12,0:23:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As a kid, I never stopped{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.50,0:23:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Searching for a great treasure{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.12,0:23:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had a map in my mind{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.88,0:23:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That I knew would lead me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.01,0:23:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had to find my way{\i0}\N{\i1}to that place{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.72,0:23:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Before someone could beat me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.22,0:23:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The promised land{\i0}\N{\i1}was in my grasp{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.85,0:23:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I wouldn't let go{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.94,0:23:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My only dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.86,0:23:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't stop chasing it{\i0}\N{\i1}until it comes true{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.49,0:23:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if the world ever changes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.79,0:23:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll call out your name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.63,0:24:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We could return to the time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.67,0:24:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When everything's the same{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.63,0:24:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as I'm with you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.89,0:24:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My memories won't fade{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.76,0:24:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Waiting for that{\i0}\N{\i1}one true dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.94,0:24:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO] I'm gonna be the\Nworld's greatest swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.78,0:24:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] Why not be the world's\Ngreatest swordsman pirate?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.28,0:24:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NWhat would you know about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.49,0:24:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,[GIRL] The soldiers have\Nstarted to go crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.66,0:24:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] Maybe because we're\Nenemies of the Marines now?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.87,0:24:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me untie your ropes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.95,0:24:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,[GIRL]\NWe have to hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.16,0:24:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There's gotta be a\Nmap of the Grand Line
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.75,0:24:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,somewhere in this base.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.29,0:24:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] Oh, uh.\NThe ropes are tighter now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.33,0:24:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZORO]\NWhat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.25,0:24:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NOn the next One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.00,0:24:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,"Morgan versus Luffy! Who's\Nthe Mysterious Pretty Girl?"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.67,0:24:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be\NKing of the Pirates!

